title: Lien Sale A lien sale will be held, pursuant to ORS87.693,
text:
Lien Sale A lien sale will be held, pursuant to ORS87.693, ad date: 10/24/2015 
Lien Sale A lien sale will be held, pursuant to ORS87.693, on Sunday, November 1, 2015 at 12:00 noon at PADDA LOK MINI STORAGE, 29836 Airport Way, Gold Beach, OR on Unit E, containing Household and Miscellaneous items belonging to the Risinger family. Publish October 24 and 31, 2015 No. 71112732
